<div id="review_42327457" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/42327457" />
    <a title="Sir He-Man" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1021324-sir-he-man"><img alt="Sir He-Man" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/42327457?book_show_action=true">Jan 08, 2009</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sir He-Man" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sir He-Man" href="/user/show/1021324-sir-he-man">Sir He-Man</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer42327457" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11727123091440575218">Oh, Ovid. What I wouldn&apos;t give to travel back in time and make sweet love to you on an island in the middle of the Mediterranean.<br/><br/>No, I don&apos;t think it&apos;s unhealthy to have lustful fantasies about Ovid. I don&apos;t care what you think! I do very much care that his work was lush, provocative and unforgettable in its revolutionary translation (often taking liberties) of what was at the time contemporary folk literature. A treasury of verse!</span>
  <span id="freeText11727123091440575218" style="display:none">Oh, Ovid. What I wouldn't give to travel back in time and make sweet love to you on an island in the middle of the Mediterranean.<br /><br />No, I don't think it's unhealthy to have lustful fantasies about Ovid. I don't care what you think! I do very much care that his work was lush, provocative and unforgettable in its revolutionary translation (often taking liberties) of what was at the time contemporary folk literature. A treasury of verse!</span>
  <a data-text-id="11727123091440575218" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review42327457">
  <td colspan="2">
    <div class="updateActionLinks">
